<blockquote>
<p>&quot;<a href="/you-may-become-science">You May Become Science</a>&quot; by Elogee FishTruck, from the <a href="http://scp-wiki.net">SCP Wiki</a>. Source: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/you-may-become-science">http://www.scpwiki.com/you-may-become-science</a>. Licensed under <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/">CC-BY-SA</a>.</p>
